   120	```
   121	
   122	### 4.3 `SurfaceAdapter`
   123	
   124	```typescript
   125	/**
   126	 * Interface implemented by the surface-specific transport integration.
   127	 * The relay foundation or product code provides this implementation.
   128	 * Surfaces package never imports a specific transport library.
   129	 */
   130	export interface SurfaceAdapter {
   131	  /**
   132	   * Send a formatted payload to the surface.
   133	   * Throws SurfaceDeliveryError if delivery fails.
   134	   */
