   225	
   226	### 4.7 `FanoutPolicy`
   227	
   228	```typescript
   229	export interface FanoutPolicy {
   230	  /**
   231	   * What to do when one surface fails during fanout.
   232	   * - 'continue': attempt all surfaces; collect errors; return FanoutResult.
   233	   * - 'abort': throw on first error; remaining surfaces are not attempted.
