   143	
   144	### v2 Consumer Notes
   145	
   146	- Policy is needed for NightCTO and MSD governance scenarios; MSD should stub the policy interface in v1 using a passthrough implementation
   147	- Examples land in v2 once the full package map is stable enough to reference confidently
   148	
